# <type>(<scope>): <subject>     (max 72 chars; imperative mood)
#
# Types:
#   feat     A new feature
#   fix      A bug fix
#   docs     Documentation only changes
#   style    Formatting; no code change
#   refactor Code change that neither fixes a bug nor adds a feature
#   perf     Performance improvement
#   test     Adding or correcting tests
#   build    Build system or external deps (npm, uv, terraform, etc.)
#   ci       CI configuration files and scripts
#   chore    Other changes that don't modify src or test files
#   revert   Reverts a previous commit
#
# Scope (optional): backend, frontend/lp, infra, deps, ...
#
# Body (optional): explain what and why, not how. Wrap at 72.
#
# Footer (optional): BREAKING CHANGE: <desc>   or   Closes #123
